HEADWORD: Interstitial
<hw>In`ter*sti"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to interstices; intermediate; within the tissues; <as>as,
<ex>interstitial</ex> cavities or spaces in the tissues of animals or
plants</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interstition</ent>⟦br⟧
